#META# contentSummary: An order sent from al-Dīwān al-Ikhtiyārī to the *muʿtamid* ʿAlī, the* silāḥ-dār*, to deliver 70 *mann* of wheat in exchange for some silk that was sold. The name of the seller and recipient of the wheat is not given, which is highly unusual. The document is complete as it ends in the date. This may be a scribal error (in inadvertent omission) or is an administrative irregularity.
